name: KQ 45
registration_message:
[TONE: FUTURE] RECEIVING TRANSMISSION

Greetings denizens of this humble galaxy! Our capital Snailship will be arriving at Logan Arcade on Friday June 27th 2025.
Get ready to tap and boogie with DJ Jivan Ivan & his holocrate of cosmic disco 45s. Prepare your best away team for tough competition on Saturday & Sunday.  Then chase that last glow of twilight Sunday night before we warp back to our homelands with berries of plenty. 

** TO SECURE A T-SHIRT YOU MUST PROVIDE YOUR SIZE BY JUNE 12TH. This is a hard deadline.

* Please make sure to read our code of conduct (linked below), you will be held to it at both Logan Arcade and Kitchen 17 at all times. Please treat both venues with respect and be harmonious guests! 

* 💸  We are asking anyone who is able, to contribute ANY AMOUNT to a ticket payment support pool. It will be spread equitably across all players who need assistance. Just enter an amount in addition to your ticket at the bottom of this form ❤️

* 🫂 if you need help with your ticket, just fill out the form and click save info instead of going through payment. We will follow up with you later if any money is due

### Thanks! We look forward to seeing you all. If you have any questions reach out to us at kqchicago@gmail.com or the discord.
payment_message: Credits Accepted. Your patronage is appreciated.

name: KQ42 : The Meaning of Life
description:
Many millions of years ago, a race of hyper-intelligent pan-dimensional beings got so fed up with the constant bickering of the meaning of life that they commissioned two of their brightest and best to design and build a stupendous super computer to calculate the answer to what is the meaning of life, the universe, and everything?
Seven and a half million years later and we have the answer: KQ42, the next installment in our Chicago tournament series.

name: KQ35
description: The Chicago Flagship tournament returns! We invite you all to beautiful summer-time Chicago for the biggest KQ tournament since BB4! The tournament will feature 4 cabs, exhibition matches, wildcard and championship brackets, fun with friends, and more.
registration_message:
## Greetings! Welcome to KQ35 Registration.

### 🚨 PLEASE READ THESE NOTES FIRST 🚨 

* 📝 You can change your information at any time while registration is open

* 💸  We are asking anyone who is able, to contribute ANY AMOUNT to a ticket payment support pool. It will be spread equitably across all players who need assistance. Just enter an amount in addition to your ticket at the bottom of this form ❤️

* 🫂 if you need help with your ticket, just fill out the form and click save info instead of going through payment. We will follow up with you later if any money is due

* 🧑‍🤝‍🧑 If your team's name is not finalized, select Free Agent and return later to create your team. Be sure to check if your team already exists before creating a new one. 

* 🗑️🐌 There is a very small quantity of limited edition TrashSnail Pins available on a first come first served basis. Payment for these will be collected separately later.

* 🧾 We are using Stripe to accept payments. You will see a charge from KQCHI MEZZOMIND.COM (the llc we are operating through). Stripe securely stores your personal data and it will not be used or shared with anyone other than to process the payment. 

### Thanks! We look forward to seeing you all. If you have any questions reach out to us at kqchicago@gmail.com or the discord.
